description:
&lt;p&gt;The post provides support to the Trust’s purchasing function utilising the ordering system to generate Purchase Orders for a wide range of goods and services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will play a key role in providing an efficient, effective, and economic procurement service to divisions and directorates within the Trust. The post holder will be responsible for supporting service delivery by ensuring timely and accurate ordering of supplies and services across a range of departments, and building an effective working relationship with service managers and requisitioners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ivan Pannell, Head of Procurement&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: ivan.pannell@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number:  03033 305267&lt;/p&gt;
